inputs.input: I need help with my order status

prompts: You are a helpful customer service agent. Help the user with their inquiry: I need help with my order status

generations.text: I'd be happy to help you check your order status. Could you please provide your order number or the email address associated with your order?

outputs.output: I'd be happy to help you check your order status. Could you please provide your order number or the email address associated with your order?

prompts: Based on the order lookup results, provide a helpful response about order ORD-12345 status: shipped, tracking: 1Z999AA1234567890, expected delivery: 2024-01-17

generations.text:
Great news! Your order #ORD-12345 has been shipped and is on its way to you. Here are the details:

• Status: Shipped
• Tracking Number: 1Z999AA1234567890
• Expected Delivery: January 17th, 2024

You can track your package using the tracking number on the carrier's website. Is there anything else I can help you with?

inputs.input: Can I change the delivery address?

prompts: User wants to change delivery address. Provide helpful guidance: Can I change the delivery address?

generations.text:
I can help you with changing your delivery address. However, the ability to modify the address depends on your order's current status:

• If your order hasn't shipped yet, we can usually update the address
• If it's already shipped, you'll need to contact the carrier directly

Could you please provide your order number so I can check the current status and see what options are available?

inputs.input: I want to return an item from my recent order

prompts: Handle return request professionally: I want to return an item from my recent order

generations.text:
I'd be happy to help you with your return. Our return policy allows returns within 30 days of delivery for most items in their original condition.

To get started, I'll need:
• Your order number
• Which item(s) you'd like to return
• The reason for the return (optional, but helps us improve)

Once I have this information, I can generate a prepaid return label and guide you through the process. What's your order number?

prompts: Provide clear information about refund timing: What's your refund processing time?

generations.text:
Our refund processing times depend on the payment method:

• **Credit/Debit Cards**: 3-5 business days after we receive the returned item
• **PayPal**: 1-2 business days after processing
• **Store Credit**: Immediate (same day)
• **Bank Transfers**: 5-7 business days

We'll send you an email confirmation once your refund has been processed. The actual time for the funds to appear in your account may vary depending on your bank or payment provider.

Do you have a specific return you're tracking?
